My name is [Dharen Paulino](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rrkja4ccIC4). I am a senior student at Burton high school and I am planning to play college basketball if any chance. I am a student athlete and I play for the school basketball team for the past four years and I have been playing for different types of basketball clubs since I started playing basketball.
